the scattering chamber and simultaneously by a monitor
detector.
Rolled carbon foil of 6.6 mg/cm2 with low
contamination of oxygen and hydrogen was used.
The dE detectors were Si surface barrier
detectors oflOO mu-m thickness. The E detectors were
Ge(Li) drifted diodes of a side-entry type with a
sensitive length of about 20 mm.
